{"tid":2200772,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天主教：我們是中華民族的兒女","createTime":"2020-09-13T08:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T09:25:58.000Z","uid":153864,"like":9,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"69b7b49d46a90c13cca5609079613d87b884b94d","tid":2200772,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"［自通識科教科書審查 連宗教科都即將淪陷？］<br />\n<br />\n自上月「通識教科書內容審查」事件，近日又爆出中小學「宗教及倫理」科的新版教科書內容偏頗。<br />\n<br />\n上圖是輯編自天主教香港教區的官方教材，內容包括：<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n禱文：天父，謝謝你讓我成為中國人，我要學耶穌般熱愛國家民族，以表示對你的感謝，Amen <br />\n（一般禱文只會承認自己是上帝的子民..）<br />\n<br />\n書中更直問：香港特首做了那件服務港人的事，令你最為欣賞呢？<br />\n（圖中的十二門徒表示震驚 可能不認同以上說話？）<br />\n</span></span><span class=\"red\"><strong><br />\n書中更有不同問題，句子引導學生要「愛國」，此書更為教區官方教材，到底「政教分離」是否快將不復存在？<br />\n<br />\n到底在以後的日子，天主教學校是否會像天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機所言，「校名再無天主教」？ <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n要對付政權一再灌輸的洗腦教育，只有學生、教師死守不退才能守住教育的最後一條防線。<br />\n不然，或許你的下一代從小便要接受「愛國愛黨」的國民教育。 <br />\n<br />\n#香港思流 #教育 #宗教 #天主教 #學生 #hkstudygram<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2vipiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2vipiz.jpg&h=9d739bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死啦 我不嬲聽都係聽人講 <br />\n「我地係上帝 天父的兒女」<br />\n睇黎係我細個學錯野 同無三權分立一鳩樣"},{"pid":"a759b3fa5b1b0aa5dc3f15d4d92f9848b8d00b9c","tid":2200772,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ee363e0052c0d7b33faab572d6af4b30ff685a","tid":2200772,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFEfaVhHSFO/?igshid=1dv9kkrmr4lwr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFEfaVhHSFO%2F%3Figshid%3D1dv9kkrmr4lwr&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513SHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=b5a8bf67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFEfaVhHSFO%2F%3Figshid%3D1dv9kkrmr4lwr&h=97e58796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFEfaVhHSFO/?igshid=1dv9kkrmr4lwr</a>"},{"pid":"5df51d7c33ddf8a30fdd688ed674c7cb26d521da","tid":2200772,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"教宗也是支那人，也要舐雜種袋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4736c3d1d7f87789c1ee2ac8dfa189e8897f9510","tid":2200772,"uid":121076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:51:46.000Z","msg":"咪好囉<br />\n求仁得仁<br />\n梵諦岡都係想咁樣姐"},{"pid":"2e20e9c6902fa056c4690fd4918ef7b951be3dfc","tid":2200772,"uid":38633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"耶穌般熱愛國家民族?<br />\n<br />\n耶穌係俾自己嘅民族釘上十字架㗎噃"},{"pid":"0fa6837b0e4f623a379d18c94293e440bad80fa8","tid":2200772,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6cb3749b4e736390bef004eb37acf8e2c45e02","tid":2200772,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T08:57